title: Rex Marks the Spot
description: A Ravenous T-Rex (the T stands for Trash-o-saurus) is on the rampage in Wharf City! Now it’s up to Tako, Wasabi, Kani, and the rest of the Sushi Pack to stop it! Based on the new hit Saturday morning television show, this Pictureback episode retelling features two sheets of stickers starring everyone’s favorite bite-sized heroes.
author: Melody Quintana
